Update.zip post-install for my HTC Vision(T-Mobile G2), an example for new android updater-script(edify), used in Clockwork Recovery 3. Apply this will:

 * Change ro.sf.lcd_density to 191 in /system/build.prop
 * Remove WIFI Calling(/system/app/MS-HTCVISION-KNT20-02.apk)
 * Remove camera click sound(/system/media/audio/ui/camera_click.ogg)
 * Change keymap, see http://forum.xda-developers.com/showthread.php?t=837002 for more info, resulting in:
	.com 		TAB
	alt-z 		^
	left softkey	\ | `
	right softkeys	[ { < ] } >

Feel free to modify and repack to update.zip using:

 $ zip -r ../postinstall-unsign.zip .

And sign the zip using jarsigner, signapk, auto-sign, zipsigner, or whatever.

Enjoy and happy playing with your Android phone.
